<div class="comment-text">
<p>“Truth is incontrovertible. Panic may resent it. Ignorance may deride it. Malice may distort it. But there it is.” Hear, hear! </p>
<p>Although it often appears from the frequent panicked, ignorant and malicious rants of the vociferous minority that ‘truth’ is becoming lost, I am confident this article represents the view of silent majority, and the overwhelming majority at that. That majority will very much applaud and appreciate your calm, well reasoned, evidence based retorts. </p>
<p>I sincerely hope you don’t feel as though you’re swimming against the current. As admirable as that trait may be, I believe you’re gliding firmly downstream. Nevertheless, someone has to simultaneously filter the toxic nonsense that floats noxiously over the surface and dredge the rubbish that has settled in the depths. Keep up the good work. ✌</p>
</div>
</div>
